text: This obsoletes IRM 1.15.27, Records and Information Management, Records Control Schedule for Compliance Research.

The material relating to the Compliance Research Records Control Schedule previously contained in IRM 1.15.27 was incorporated into the November 2017 revision of Document 12990, Records and Information Management Records Control Schedules.
IRM 1.15.27 dated November 1, 2002 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
Director, Identity and Records Protection (IRP) Privacy, Governmental Liaison and Disclosure (PGLD)
